'''澳大利亞高速鐵路'''（{{lang-en|'''High-speed rail in Australia'''}}） 為[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]規劃中的高速鐵路工程，早自1980年代就啟動興建案評估。{{sfn|Williams|1998}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.crikey.com.au/theurbanist/2014/04/23/bze-how-we-found-high-speed-rail-to-be-commercially-viable/ |title=[[Crikey|Crikey]] - BZE: How we found high speed rail to be commercially viable |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2014-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424125451/http://blogs.crikey.com.au/theurbanist/2014/04/23/bze-how-we-found-high-speed-rail-to-be-commercially-viable/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>澳大利亞政府2013年公布興建評估報告書，計畫連結[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]、[[坎培拉|坎培拉]]、[[悉尼|悉尼]]和[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]等澳洲東海岸城市<ref name=HSRDoIT>{{cite web|url=http://www.infrastructure.gov.au/rail/trains/high_speed/index.aspx|title=High Speed Rail|publisher=[[Department_of_Infrastructure_and_Transport|Department of Infrastructure and Transport]]|archivedate=2013年8月14日|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814201622/http://www.infrastructure.gov.au/rail/trains/high_speed/index.aspx|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，全长1,748公里。部分人士則主張路線應延伸至[[阿德萊德|阿德萊德]]<ref>{{citation | title = Adelaide must be in high-speed rail loop | first = Christopher | last = Russell | date = 2011年1月31日1 | url = http://www.adelaidenow.com.au/business/adelaide-must-been-in-high-speed-rail-loop/story-e6frede3-1225997604502 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120701083422/http://www.adelaidenow.com.au/business/adelaide-must-been-in-high-speed-rail-loop/story-e6frede3-1225997604502 | archivedate = 2012年7月1日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name=Baillieu>{{citation | title = Baillieu pushes high-speed rail links | author = Clay Lucas | publisher = The Age | date = 2010年9月23日 | url = http://www.theage.com.au/victoria/baillieu-pushes-highspeed-rail-links-20101123-184p9.html | location = Melbourne | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106121844/http://www.theage.com.au/victoria/baillieu-pushes-highspeed-rail-links-20101123-184p9.html | archivedate = 2012年11月6日 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>或延伸到澳洲大陸西岸的[[珀斯|珀斯]]。<ref>{{Cite web
